"Test — $area en multirow nativo
'<hr/>
'<h4>1-row simple — debe funcionar</h4>
V = [$area{x^2 @ x = 0 : 1}; $area{x @ x = 0 : 2}]
'V ='V
'<h4>2-row direct — ¿funciona?</h4>
M = [$area{x^2 @ x = 0 : 1}; $area{x^3 @ x = 0 : 1}|$area{x @ x = 0 : 2}; $area{x^2 @ x = 0 : 2}]
'M ='M
'<h4>2-row con valores intermedios</h4>
a1 = $area{x^2 @ x = 0 : 1}
a2 = $area{x^3 @ x = 0 : 1}
a3 = $area{x @ x = 0 : 2}
a4 = $area{x^2 @ x = 0 : 2}
M2 = [a1; a2|a3; a4]
'M2 ='M2
